introduction 1 bhp billiton direct reduced iron pty ltd (dri), formerly known as bhp direct reduced iron pty ltd and bhp development finance pty ltd (development finance), and bhp billiton finance ltd (finance) are wholly owned subsidiaries of bhp billiton ltd (bhp) formerly bhp limited.
the bhp and billiton plc merger which resulted in the name changes occurred in 2001.
